18
19 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF ARKANSAS:
20
21 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code § 23-99-203(d), concerning the definition of
22 "healthcare provider" under the Patient Protection Act of 1995, is amended to
23 read as follows:
24 (d) "Healthcare provider" means those individuals or entities licensed
25 by the State of Arkansas to provide healthcare services, limited to the
26 following:
27 (1) Advanced practice nurses;
28 (2) Athletic trainers;
29 (3) Audiologists;
30 (4) Certified behavioral health providers;
31 (5) Certified orthotists;
32 (6) Chiropractors;
33 (7) Community mental health centers or clinics;
34 (8) Dentists;
35 (9) Home health care;
36 (10) Hospice care;
